{"tid":521450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江老婦羽絨突爆炸　消防員：或因靜電煤氣反應 (12:07)","createTime":"2018-01-06T14:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T14:44:55.000Z","uid":145589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ee9712d856d43dbba62b1816460780d10c0b00","tid":521450,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"浙江一名老婆婆周四（4日）在廚房收拾東西時，身穿的羽絨突然爆炸，衣服背面出現了幾個洞，幸好她沒有大礙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/06/223532_e790ee046e9ea1b8e7cd8f1f210b7b94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F06%2F223532_e790ee046e9ea1b8e7cd8f1f210b7b94.jpg&h=6e78f478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老婆婆的老伴張爺爺指，當時他正在房間整理行李，突然聽到廚房有一大聲響，以為是煤氣爆炸，豈料老婆婆呼喊：「嚇死了，嚇死了！」原來是老婆婆的羽絨突然「爆炸了」。除了羽絨外套被燒外，廚房的煤氣罐旁邊的毛巾和垃圾袋，都有一定程度燒過痕迹。<br />\n<br />\n浙江青田消防中隊消防員吳嘉華解釋，可能是因為煤氣泄漏達到一定的濃度，然後羽絨產生靜電，導致羽絨爆炸。他指，冬天天氣較乾燥，很多衣物會產生靜電，與煤氣有反應的話，可能產生爆炸，呼籲市民要多加留意，用完煤氣要及時關上。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180106/s00004/1515208219280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180106%2Fs00004%2F1515208219280&d=p%2BsVDQEEkqe1gYArcpEg2W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=dcbb1c86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180106%2Fs00004%2F1515208219280&h=74f2efe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180106/s00004/1515208219280</a>"},{"pid":"5a97829654353b59948326587540a23404e79c8e","tid":521450,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca1a6819d42fe1bf18da1845b2a5b1480b7d12a","tid":521450,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:36:56.000Z","msg":"中國的都會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ab5ff136f3aeb6a8aa76e9364a3dbd66a2f97b","tid":521450,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"羽絨都可以爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然強國"},{"pid":"bd4ac1bd76c4b7126b0420f254578ee0b2bcbec7","tid":521450,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1f79d3b0c8949201d3e411cca94c7880c40329","tid":521450,"uid":145589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羽絨都可以爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然強國</blockquote><br />\n有冇人知道到底點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}